 1999-16161999-09-280HERITAGE,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ROBERT THOMAS ROSS, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Tony Tascona, whose term has expired.
